maneuvers.narrative: Start out going west on Acoma Blvd toward Highway 95/AZ-95.
Turn right onto Highway 95/AZ-95. Continue to follow AZ-95 N.
Stay straight to go onto I-40 W (Crossing into California).
Merge onto US-95 N via EXIT 133 toward Searchlight/Las Vegas (Crossing into Nevada).
Merge onto US-95 N/US-93 N toward Las Vegas/Henderson.
Merge onto I-15 N via EXIT 76B toward Salt Lake City (Passing through Arizona, then crossing into Utah).
Merge onto I-15 N via EXIT 379 toward Pocatello (Passing through Idaho, then crossing into Montana).
Merge onto I-15 N via EXIT 129 toward Helena (Crossing into Alberta, Canada).
I-15 N becomes Red Coat Trail/AB-4 N.
Turn right onto Mayor Magrath Dr/Red Coat Trail/AB-4.
Merge onto AB-3 W toward Calgary/Ft Macleod.
Turn right onto AB-3/AB-2.
Merge onto AB-2 N toward Calgary.
Merge onto Anthony Henday Dr/AB-216 W via the exit on the left toward West Edmonton Mall.
Merge onto TC-16 W via EXIT 25 toward Jasper.
Merge onto AB-43 N via EXIT 340 toward Grande Prairie/Whitecourt/Peace River.
AB-43 N becomes Highway 43X/AB-43X. Pass through 1 roundabout.
Keep right at the fork to continue on Highway 43X/AB-43X.
Turn slight right onto Township Road 714/AB-43. Continue to follow AB-43 (Crossing into British Columbia).
AB-43 becomes BC-2.
Turn right onto 50th St/BC-2. Continue to follow BC-2.
Enter next roundabout and take the 3rd exit onto Alaska Ave.
Alaska Ave becomes BC-97 (Crossing into Yukon).
BC-97 becomes Alaska Hwy (Passing through British Columbia, Yukon, British Columbia, Yukon, British Columbia, Yukon and British Columbia, then crossing into Yukon).
Stay straight to go onto Alaska Hwy/YT-1. Continue to follow YT-1.
Turn right onto Alaska Hwy/YT-1. Continue to follow Alaska Hwy (Crossing into Alaska, United States).
Turn left onto Glenn Highway Tok Cutoff/AK-1. Continue to follow AK-1.
Turn left onto Richardson Highway/Richardson Hwy/AK-4/AK-1.
Turn slight right onto Glenn Hwy/AK-1. Continue to follow AK-1 S.
Stay straight to go onto E 5th Ave.
Turn left onto L St.
Turn left onto W 6th Ave.
Welcome to ANCHORAGE, AK.
